SWCore:
enable
configure terminal
hostname SWCore
vtp domain GESTAO_WAN
vtp mode server
vtp password cisco
vlan 10
 name DATA
vlan 20
 name WLAN_USERS
vlan 99
 name MANAGEMENT
exit
interface range gi1/1/1-2, gi1/0/1-2, gi1/1/3
 switchport mode trunk
 switchport trunk native vlan 99



. WLAN (WPA2 Enterprise + RADIUS)

Esta configuração é feita no WLC. No Packet Tracer, a interface gráfica é mais comum, mas aqui estão os parâmetros lógicos:

    WLC Management: Atribuir IP na VLAN de Gestão.

    RADIUS Server: Apontar para o IP do servidor AAA na Cloud Privada.

        Shared Secret: radius_key (ou a definida no server).

    WLAN Config:

        SSID: WLAN_CORP

        Security: WPA2 + 802.1X (Enterprise).

        Auth Server: Selecionar o servidor RADIUS configurado.

    No Servidor AAA (Cloud):

        Service: RADIUS (On).

        Client: IP do WLC | Password: radius_key.

        User Setup: User: user_wlan | Pass: wlanpass.

SWcore_a:
enable
configure terminal
hostname SWCore_a


vtp domain GESTAO_WAN
vtp mode client
vtp password cisco



interface range gi1/1/1-2
 channel-group 1 mode active
 switchport mode trunk
 switchport trunk native vlan 99


interface range gi1/1/3-4
 channel-group 2 mode active
 switchport mode trunk
 switchport trunk native vlan 99


interface vlan 99
 ip address 10.1.51.3 255.255.252.0
 no shutdown
exit
ip default-gateway 10.1.48.1


aaa new-model
radius-server host 192.168.48.12 key radius_key
aaa authentication login SSH_AUTH group radius local
line vty 0 15
 transport input ssh
 login authentication SSH_AUTH
exit

